1 SENATE FLOOR VERSION
February 23, 2026
2
3 SENATE BILL NO. 2071 By: Murdock of the Senate
4 and
5 Newton of the House
6
7
8 An Act relating to agriculture; amending 2 O.S. 2021,
Sections 7-401, 7-403, 7-415, and 7-421, which relate
9 to the Oklahoma Milk and Milk Products Act; updating
statutory references; modifying definitions;
10 increasing fees for production and sale of certain
milk products; clarifying jurisdictional authority of
11 dairy inspection and grading programs; updating
statutory language; and providing an effective date.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 2 O.S. 2021, Section 7-401, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 7-401. Sections 4 7-401 through 23 7-421 of this act
18 title shall be known and may be cited as the “Oklahoma Milk and Milk
19 Products Act”.
20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 2 O.S. 2021, Section 7-403, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 7-403. As used in the Oklahoma Milk and Milk Products
23 Act:
24
